headline: ClearBridge Large Cap Growth Strategy Sold Intercontinental Exchange (ICE) as The Stock Re-Rated
summary: ClearBridge Investments, an investment management company, released its “ClearBridge Large Cap Growth Strategy” first quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. The majority of growth indexes entered correction territory during the quarter, due to pressure from the chaotic tariff implementation, concerns about a weakening U.S. economy, and increased inflation.
